{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"dynamic"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"detectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/detectionRate"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in normal performance mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to 20, meaning that 20 frames per second are detected\/recognized, equally distributed over one second."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 10 frames will be skipped and 20 frames will be detected\/recognized."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate."}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"detectionRate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su"}],"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)detectionRate","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"detectionRate"}],"title":"detectionRate"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/detectionrate"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/detectionrate"]}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK":{"title":"ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Version: 8.0.1"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/detectionRate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in normal performance mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to 20, meaning that 20 frames per second are detected\/recognized, equally distributed over one second."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 10 frames will be skipped and 20 frames will be detected\/recognized."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate."}],"title":"detectionRate","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"detectionRate","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/detectionrate","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"detectionRate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/detectionRate","role":"symbol"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotbarcodescannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"value":"occ","op":"replace","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage"},{"value":"Instance Property","op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading"},{"value":"detectionRate","op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/title"},{"value":"property","op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind"},{"value":[{"text":"detectionRate","kind":"identifier"}],"op":"replace","path":"\/metadata\/fragments"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/topicSections"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/relationshipsSections"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/seeAlsoSections"},{"value":{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSUInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSUInteger"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"detectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},"op":"replace","path":"\/primaryContentSections\/0"},{"value":"detectionRate","op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotBarcodeScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConf